.container
  .row
    div.col-md-8
      div.center-block
        img.img-responsive.center-block(src='/assets/images/welcome.gif')

      p
        | We at Kids 4 Truth are glad you're here! EquipU is our online library of <strong>free children's ministry
        | resources</strong>, put together for parents, church leaders, youth workers, and others working with children
        | worldwide. EquipU is a massive compendium of relevant, fine-tuned materials designed to help you teach
        | children God-focused truth in a God-focused way.
      p
        | Since it is web-based, EquipU facilitates efficient support and community discussion. It is a place where
        | workers can find materials and interact with one another to share tips and tools that have improved their own
        | ministries.

      div.center-block
        h3.subTitleDark.text-center GET
          = ' '
          span.subTitleLight STARTED
        img.img-responsive.center-block(src='/assets/images/line.gif')

      p Again, EquipU is <strong>free</strong>. The following items are a few highlights of EquipU's features:

      h4.subTitleDark TRUTHTIME TEACHER
        = ' '
        span.subTitleLight LESSON PLANS
      p
        | We are constantly developing new and updated teacher lesson plans. Inside EquipU, you will find a document
        | library that contains the most up-to-date collection of lesson plans and other official, clubs-specific,
        |staff-designed teacher resources.

      h4.subTitleDark USER
        = ' '
        span.subTitleLight CONTRIBUTIONS
      p
        | Many people use the Kids 4 Truth curriculum in different ways to meet their own various ministry needs.
        | Different approaches to the same "problem" may work better in different situations. On EquipU, you will find
        | materials that have been created and contributed by other children's ministry workers who want to share what
        | they have found helpful in their environment. These resources include things such as attendance sheets,
        | training resources, ideas for activities, and more.

      h4.subTitleDark MUCH
        = ' '
        span.subTitleLight MORE!
      p
        | We are constantly posting improvements and updating the resources on EquipU. Streaming video and audio
        | training sessions from the Kids 4 Truth staff, surveys and results, feedback forms, etc. are all available
        | here on EquipU. We would love to have you learning right along with us!

    div.col-md-4
      div.panel.panel-default
        div.panel-heading
          h4.panel-title Kids 4 Truth Blogs

        div.panel-body
          p As we look for different ways to communicate with our users, we have been regularly publishing to a series
            | of blogs. You can visit those blogs by clicking the links below:
          ul
            li
              a(href='http://blog.kids4truth.com/clubsblog/') Clubs Blog
            li
              a(href='http://blog.kids4truth.com/') Ministry Blog

      div.panel.panel-default
        div.panel-heading
          h4.panel-title Key Resources
        div.panel-body
          p The following is a list of resources that nearly every club can use:
          ul
            li
              a(href='http://equipu.kids4truth.com/files/folders/director_start_up_manuals/entry3994.aspx')
                | Director's Startup Manual - Traditional Club
            li
              a(href='http://equipu.kids4truth.com/files/folders/director_start_up_manuals/entry5293.aspx')
                | Director's Startup Manual - Focused Group Study


